description._content: Description: Nurseries made during August to receive seeds. Pagalan River runs between nurseries and trees in background. Posts and wire netting separate the old from the new nurseries. (Taken 14/8/06) Location: Borneo Date: 14 August 1906 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Interior of older nursery - 1st.batch of seeds planted put covered with mats and under shades made of large leaves. On the right pipe for carrying water from the Pagalan. In the background top of the Manager's House. (Taken 18/8/06.) Location: Borneo Date: 18 August 1906 ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/528.
